<HEADLINE>
FT  20 FEB 92 / Toshiba cuts pre-tax profit forecast
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Toshiba, the Japanese electronics group, early today cut its forecast for
group pre-tax profit in the year to end-March to Y110bn (Pounds 491m) from
Y195bn predicted in November. Actual group pre-tax profit totalled Y259bn
the previous year.
