<DOCNO>FT921-7993</DOCNO>
<PROFILE>_AN-CBUBOAACFT</PROFILE>
<DATE>920220
</DATE>
<HEADLINE>
FT  20 FEB 92 / World News in Brief: Singapore libel appeal
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Veteran Singapore opposition politician Joshua Jeyaretnam appealed against a
high court order directing him to pay libel damages, costs and interest
totalling SDollars 652,000 (Dollars 398,000) to former Singapore prime
minister Lee Kuan Yew.
</TEXT>
