Festivals, carnivals, cultural and sporting events in 1992
Hong Kong's calendar has a rich diversity of special events. In January they
included the Hong Kong Fringe Festival; the 20th Hong Kong Arts Festival and
the First Pacific Bank Tennis Challenge.
February 4 saw celebrations for the Chinese New Year (the Year of the
Monkey), with a New Year Firework Display on February 5. Other events in the
month included the Hong Kong/Shenzhen International Marathon; and the Spring
Lantern Festival.
