Airline check-in times
Most airlines start check-in procedures about two hours before departure,
while some offer early check-in service.
CATHAY PACIFIC: Passengers can check in at Cathay's Citycheck centre
(Pacific Place, Queensway, Hong Kong tel. 747 1788) from 8:00am to 8:00pm
one day before the flight until 3 hours before departure time. First class,
business class and Marco Polo Club members travelling with hand baggage only
can check in by telephone (747 7877) up to 50 minutes before departure.
UNITED AIRLINES: Passengers can check in one day before departure at
airline's two ticketing offices (11:00am-6:00pm) but luggage must be checked
at the airport 2 hours before the flight.
BRITISH AIRWAYS: Check-in service for evening flights starts at 3:30pm on
day of travel.
Airport tax
An airport tax of HKDollars 150 is levied on departure. The size of carry-on
hand-baggage should be limited to 9 ins by 14 ins by22 ins, weighing no more
than five kilogrammes.
