The two men, Mr Abdel Baset Ali Mohammed Al-Megrahi and Mr Al-Amin Khalifa
Fhimah, appeared before the media in a meeting room at the Libyan Supreme
Court. The appearance, which followed what Judge Ahmed al-Zawi described as
