Andrei Kozyrev, Russian foreign minister, discuss their meeting in Moscow
yesterday which focused on reduction of strategic weapons. The White House
later said President George Bush and Russian President Boris Yeltsin were
likely to hold their first formal summit meeting in July in Washington
(Omitted).
